## here() starts at /Users/April30/benchmark-hdf5-clustering
new_mem <- read.csv("/Users/April30/benchmark-hdf5-clustering/ongoing_analysis/ChunkTest/TENxBrainData/Output/new_mem.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",")
new_mem %>% 
  filter(calc_label=="full") %>%
  filter(observations==75000 | observations==500000) %>%
  dplyr::group_by(observations, abs.batch.size, label2) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = as.factor(abs.batch.size), y = memory, color = label2)) +
          #geom_line()+
          geom_point()+
          labs(title = "HDF5 Geometry: Memory for the Whole Process") + 
  facet_grid(~observations)

new_mem %>% 
  filter(calc_label=="FALSE") %>%
  filter(observations==75000 | observations==500000) %>%
  dplyr::group_by(observations, abs.batch.size, label2) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = as.factor(abs.batch.size), y = memory, color = label2)) +
          #geom_line()+
          geom_point()+
          labs(title = "HDF5 Geometry: Memory for Computing Centorids") + 
  facet_grid(~observations)

new_mem %>% 
  filter(calc_label=="TRUE") %>%
  filter(observations==75000 | observations==500000) %>%
  dplyr::group_by(observations, abs.batch.size, label2) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = as.factor(abs.batch.size), y = memory, color = label2)) +
          #geom_line()+
          geom_point()+
          labs(title = "HDF5 Geometry: Memory for Predicting Labels") + 
  facet_grid(~observations)

new_time <- read.csv("/Users/April30/benchmark-hdf5-clustering/ongoing_analysis/ChunkTest/TENxBrainData/Output/new_time.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",")
